{
  "stem": "2460.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, just isolated streets.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And between the-- between the-- the-- the front and the beginning of the street and end of the street was just barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some Hungarian soldiers were watching it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the people that were watching it were not really dressed as soldiers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They [? wore ?] civilian clothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had, I think, the Hungarian banner on that the Hungarian had, something like this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not the Arrow Cross.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In our city was no-- no functioning Arrow Cross.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were people belong to the Arrow Cross, and they were shouting this, dirty Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But was no official-- I don't remember that they were parading like the Arrow Cross.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We couldn't leave those-- those streets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, of course not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, of course not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the war came to me that, in 1938, the Czechoslovakian Army was mobilizing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was a sergeant in the Czechoslovakian Army, and he was mobilized.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was very proud of him when I saw him all dressed up as a soldier.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were-- they were taken to the train station.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everything moved by trains then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was happy, but I was also crying that the father left.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they went somewhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can't remember where they-- where they took them exactly because when he wrote to us, he had only army numbers, no addresses.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So when the Hungarians [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] took over Levice, he was in the Czechoslovakian Army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we were terrible concerned that the father is in the Czechoslovakian Army, and we are already in Hungaria.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But three or four months later, we get orders that-- I mean, news that older parents-- I mean, fathers and children, that they left the Czechoslovakian Army.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
